  "text": "Similar with other Thermococcales species, Pa. pacificus possesses an incomplete tricarboxylic acid (TCA) cycle, a modified Embden-Meyerhof pathway to glycolysis and metabolism pathway of proteins and carbohydrates (3-7). The conserved respiration system is also represented by membrane-bound hydrogenase and A 0 A 1 -type ATP synthase [CITATION_1] .",
